parameters: 歩行紅
歩行紅
歩行紅
歩行紅

\FF[iruka_smile]Iruka: "I totally thought you were going to quit the
Detective Club and start something like an Agent Club."

\FF[inu_smile]Maple: "Right. I even secretly went on a diet to fit into
that suit."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Were you planning to disband the Detective Club? Was
that the intention of the former club president and the
advisor teacher...?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "After all, it's the same thing, right? It's a club
activity to solve troubles at the academy."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[2]Maple: "Yes. And it's not certain that no more mysterious
beings will appear. Rather... they're bound to keep coming,
right?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[2]Maple: "If we hadn't managed to get the Iris Blade in time,
it would have been a global crisis. That's a huge
responsibility."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "I don't think there was such a club as the Detective
Club... And aren't you two getting a bit too carried away?
This is a school where... we're supposed to study..."
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "A place to flirt with your lover?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[2]Maple: "Right. After being shown so much right in front of
us... you know."
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "L-lover?!?"
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "Aren't you dating Shiratora-san?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[2]Maple: "Could it be... you're not? Was it just that you
became honest when you transformed into a mysterious being,
and now everything's back to normal?"
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "That is..."
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Well... how should I put it..."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "I've never used words like 'lover' or 'dating'... or
anything like going on a date..."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "I see! So you're going to start using them a lot
from now on."
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[2]Maple: "It's not just youth. Enjoy your firsts, Akane-san."
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Auuu..."

\FF[yurisu_smile]Yurika: "Sorry for being late. I didn't mean to keep you
waiting."
\FF[yurisu_smile]Yurika: "Be happy, Sirius"

\FF[yurisu_smile]Yurika: "Agent Regulus has officially recognized our joining
of 'Banter'. It seems we were evaluated for saving the
academy and our adaptability to the suits."

\FF[nakosu_smile]Nadeshiko: "I was worried that only Yurika-san would pass,
but I'm glad! Now we can be together at school and as
agents, Akane."

\FF[nakosu_smile]Nadeshiko: "Ah! Should I call you Sirius when you're dressed
like this?"

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "No, Akane is fine. Regulus and Acrux might be
reluctant, but I am Akane Suzaku."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Then, I'd like to call you Akane too. Of course,
you can call me Yurika without any honorifics... to make it
more friendly."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "I'd rather not... I'm used to calling you
president... so let's keep it that way..."
\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Then I'll call you... Yurika..."
\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Ah, Nadeshiko. I'm happy... It feels fresh!"

\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "But... indeed... it might be embarrassing at
first..."

\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "More importantly... if you passed, then both of you
got assigned code names, right? I want to know! My favorite
Summer Triangle is already taken."

\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[inu_trouble]\AA[2]Maple: "There are only 23 of them, and there are still
vacancies? And yet they start with minor ones like Regulus
and Acrux... What kind of organization is this?"

\F[yurisu_smile]\FF[inu_trouble]\AA[1]Yurika: "Interesting point of view, teacher. We still don't
fully understand the organization, but fighting against
mysterious beings is certain."

\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[inu_trouble]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Then... let me introduce mine! My code name
is..."

\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[inu_trouble]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Spica! The brightest star in Virgo! Please take
care of Agent Spica!"

\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "It suits you, Shiratora-san! That suit is a perfect
match for you!"

\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[2]Maple: "That makes me wonder about Arcturus. Spica and
Arcturus are husband and wife stars..."
\F[sirius_angry]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Grrr... There's no such person!"

\F[yurisu_smile]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[1]Yurika: "Then, let me also introduce mine. My code name is
Antares. Agent Antares."

\F[yurisu_smile]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "As expected of the president. The image of a red
star suits you perfectly."

\F[yurisu_smile]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[2]Maple: "Yes! I thought it would be Aldebaran or something
like that for you! Because if we're talking about
strength... right?"

\F[yurisu_smile]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[1]Yurika: "I've never heard of having a red image before...
but I'm happy to be called strong. What do you think,
Akane?"
\F[yurisu_smile]\FF[sirius_smile]\AA[2]Akane: "I think it suits you. Yu, Yurika..."

\F[yurisu_smile]\FF[sirius_smile]\AA[1]Yurika: "Thank you! Being called by my name is... certainly
embarrassing..."

\F[yurisu_smile]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "Then what should I choose for myself? Maybe...
Betelgeuse to match Suzaku-san?"

\F[yurisu_smile]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[2]Maple: "That's a good idea. Then I'll be Procyon. That way,
we'll be friends with Sirius in the Winter Triangle."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Fuh, I hope neither of you will come to any danger!
Geez..."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_angry]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "So, that being said... I can't just ignore the
'friends' comment! Spica can only be seen from the Southern
Hemisphere, so it's not beside Sirius!"
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[nakosu_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "You're surprisingly... concerned about it..."
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Yeah..."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Antares is also in the Southern Hemisphere... It's
truly regrettable not to be by Akane's side..."
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Yurika still cares about... me...?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Of course. There's no problem even if Nadeshiko and
I are in love. It's my duty to make an effort to be liked by
you."
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "So you're saying... you won't give up?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "It means we won't compete... won't fight over it.
I'll make an effort so that Akane can accept both of us.
Because Akane is the most important to me, I don't want to
confuse her."
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "As expected... your love is heavy..."
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "..."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "By the way, was there any information on that masked
villain?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[2]Maple: "I'm curious too. He might still be at this school,
right?"

\F[yurisu_angry]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[1]Yurika: "The secret society Revildo... we still don't know
anything yet..."

\F[yurisu_angry]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[1]Yurika: "They are the masterminds behind this series of
incidents. Because... I've also encountered them."

\F[yurisu_angry]\FF[nakosu_angry]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "I knew it! That man turned Yurika into a
monster!"

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[nakosu_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "So Soga, Wata, and Ama as well... What's their
purpose?"

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[yurisu_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "It's certain they're using this school for
something. Creating powerful monsters for world domination
doesn't seem like a far-fetched idea."
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[nakosu_angry]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "We can't let them run loose..."
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[nakosu_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "I know. This time we'll catch them ourselves."
\F[sirius_angry2]\\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Yes. With Akane and us, we can do it."
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "I think so too. Everyone, let's do our best!"
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Yeah!"
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Of course."
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "Though I may fall short..."
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[inu_smile]\AA[2]Maple: "Let's work hard."
